    "text": "Suspect Arrested with Narcotics \u2013 Daulagala Police On the night of 23.03.2026, officers from the Daulagala Police Station carried out a raid in the Alapalawala area of the Daulagala Police Division, based on received intelligence. During the operation, a suspect was arrested for the illegal possession, transportation, and distribution of 301 narcotic substances without a valid license. The suspect is a 40-year-old resident of Muruthalawa. Daulagala Police are conducting ongoing investigations. 03. \u0db4\u0dbd\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0dae\u0dba \u0dba\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0dd0\u0daf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 \u0dc3\u0dd4 \u0dd0\u0daf \u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0da7 - \u0dd9\u0d82\u0dd9\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca",
