    "text": "\u0baa\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bca\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 Fatal Road Accident \u2013 Hanwella Police Division On the night of 23.03.2026, a motorcycle traveling towards Avissawella collided with an oncoming lorry in the Ilukkumbura area along the old Kaduwela\u2013Avissawella road, within the Hanwella Police Division. Both the rider and the pillion passenger sustained critical injuries and were admitted to hospital. The pillion rider later succumbed to injuries. The deceased is a 22-year-old resident of Avissawella. The lorry driver involved in the accident has been taken into custody. Hanwella Police are conducting further inquiries. Police Media Division",
